Body:
test_strings = [
    "I think you're a fucking terrible person. I won't apologise for it.",
    'Shit, this is the greatest thing ever. I luv the interwebs.']
foul_words, context = Insults.foul_language(test_strings)
assert_equal(foul_words, ['fucking', 'shit'])
assert_equal(context, ["I think you're a fucking terrible person.",
    'Shit, this is the greatest'])
